  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DuaLight </strong> is a challenging cyberpunk platformer with an intense soundtrack. Switch between day and night environments, go through dangerous obstacles by manipulating gravity and time, upgrade your abilities and conquer the levels. Be ready for the ultimate adrenaline rush.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Switch between day-to-night regimes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ability to switch between day and night regimes serves as the central feature of the game. This dramatically changes the environment and gives players a distinct moveset for each time period. It also alters the way some obstacles move and function. Through this, the player will be able to overcome challenges and beat levels in different ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/0de052e50bed288e6f7cddc3f1118d4f.poster.avif?t=1734622326\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/0de052e50bed288e6f7cddc3f1118d4f.webm?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/0de052e50bed288e6f7cddc3f1118d4f.mp4?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast-paced Movement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will receive various abilities that they can mix and match to make the game easier, helping them overcome different and larger obstacles. This will allow players to discover different strategies for completing the same level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/21f285848fc4cdf84b4ce3d481c9cf7f.poster.avif?t=1734622326\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/21f285848fc4cdf84b4ce3d481c9cf7f.webm?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/21f285848fc4cdf84b4ce3d481c9cf7f.mp4?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ability Upgrades</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the players finish levels, they’ll earn points. These points will allow them to upgrade and enhance their abilities. This will make them more agile and open up new ways to use and combine their powers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/67fbbbb2eadd44435f18bd6cdcf6fa69.poster.avif?t=1734622326\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/67fbbbb2eadd44435f18bd6cdcf6fa69.webm?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/67fbbbb2eadd44435f18bd6cdcf6fa69.mp4?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DuaLight </strong> is a challenging cyberpunk platformer with an intense soundtrack. Switch between day and night environments, go through dangerous obstacles by manipulating gravity and time, upgrade your abilities and conquer the levels. Be ready for the ultimate adrenaline rush.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Switch between day-to-night regimes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ability to switch between day and night regimes serves as the central feature of the game. This dramatically changes the environment and gives players a distinct moveset for each time period. It also alters the way some obstacles move and function. Through this, the player will be able to overcome challenges and beat levels in different ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/0de052e50bed288e6f7cddc3f1118d4f.poster.avif?t=1734622326\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/0de052e50bed288e6f7cddc3f1118d4f.webm?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/0de052e50bed288e6f7cddc3f1118d4f.mp4?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast-paced Movement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will receive various abilities that they can mix and match to make the game easier, helping them overcome different and larger obstacles. This will allow players to discover different strategies for completing the same level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/21f285848fc4cdf84b4ce3d481c9cf7f.poster.avif?t=1734622326\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/21f285848fc4cdf84b4ce3d481c9cf7f.webm?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/21f285848fc4cdf84b4ce3d481c9cf7f.mp4?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ability Upgrades</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the players finish levels, they’ll earn points. These points will allow them to upgrade and enhance their abilities. This will make them more agile and open up new ways to use and combine their powers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/67fbbbb2eadd44435f18bd6cdcf6fa69.poster.avif?t=1734622326\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/67fbbbb2eadd44435f18bd6cdcf6fa69.webm?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841750/extras/67fbbbb2eadd44435f18bd6cdcf6fa69.mp4?t=1734622326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
